## Object System and Methods
The LiebrechtPackage implements the S3 object system in R.
Specifically, the lp_cor object (Liebrecht Correlation object) includes two S3 methods:
- print.lp_cor() - Displays a summary of the correlation matrix
- plot.lp_cor() - Creates a correlation heatmap 
